<h1>Hello <%= @freelancer.name %>,</h1>

<p>
  Congratulations! You have successfully accepted the task "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>" on Gighive.
</p>

<h3>Task Details</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Title:</strong> <%= @task.title %></li>
  <li><strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %></li>
  <li><strong>Budget:</strong> <%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ", format: "%u%n") %></li>
  <li><strong>Deadline:</strong> <%= @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
</ul>

<p>
  Please coordinate with the client to ensure timely completion of the task. Meeting the deadline will help build trust and strengthen your profile on Gighive.
</p>

<p>
  For more information or to manage the task, click the link below:
  <%= link_to 'View Task on Gighive', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none;' %>
</p>

<p>
  We wish you a successful and productive collaboration! Thank you for being a valued member of Gighive.
</p>

<p>
  Best Regards,<br>
  <strong>The Gighive Team</strong>
</p>
